
Name:    pinentry
Version: 1.1.0
Release: 6%{?dist}
Summary: Collection of simple PIN or passphrase entry dialogs

License: GPLv2+
URL:     http://www.gnupg.org/aegypten/
Source0: ftp://ftp.gnupg.org/gcrypt/pinentry/%{name}-%{version}.tar.bz2
